## Introduction
- The LFS system will be built by using an already installed Linux distribution
- setting VM
	- 20 GB of dynamic memory (for debian system)
	- 4 processors 
	- 8 GB of RAM
	- network bridge
- install debian on VM
- setting up ssh connection by bridge
```
nano /etc/ssh/sshd_config
PermitRootLogin yes (change value)
```
